Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A racing second hand, a shooting comet,\Na wind-up doll, and a crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystery-solving logic\Ndrenches the walls of dry hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.08,0:00:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's case is the\Nfirst original TV 2-parter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayor! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did last night's storm carry it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:46.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryujin-Maru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Isn't that the boat\Nthat was lost seven years ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was 1 billion yen\Nin gold on that ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing onboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!\NWhere did all the gold go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you suppose\Nit turned up only now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like a ghost ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be the Suigun curse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools! There is no curse!\NIt's just a dumb superstition!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ghost Ship Murder Case (Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:41.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ghost Ship Murder Case (Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll land on Shikishima in three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We greatly appreciate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:51.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Goro Kinoshita (53)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your coming all the way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to give a lecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it certainly is a long way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Kinoshita-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear a ship that went missing\Nwith 1 billion yen in gold onboard
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,recently turned up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! People on the\Nisland think it's a ghost ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the money never turned up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. We're not even sure\Nthere really was any onboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mayor is just glad that the\Ntown has garnered a lot of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost ship garnering attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! And that's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inviting someone so famous\Nis another way of gaining prestige!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My reputation extends this far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of Japan knows about the\Ngreat detective Kogoro Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He works for a Tokyo travel agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to create a tour\Ncentered around the ghost ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:18.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikishima Island
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Detective Mori!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:33.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Kogoro Mori-sensei!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a warm welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-{\i1}sensei{\i0}! Thank you\Nfor coming all this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mayor Mikami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We welcome you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this lame guy really famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you\Nwould've been a lot cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say, kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzu-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Don't be rude\Nto Daddy's guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a lovely daughter you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan. Conan Edogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a weird name.\NIs that the trend in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Suzu Mikami! It looks like\NI'm a little older than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being with younger people is trendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the travel agent--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Uehara from Toto Travel Agency.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise! We'll help in\Nany way to bring tourists here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the ghost ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks. I'll look for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship was on\Nthe ocean floor for years
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but only has barnacles\Non its underside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy! It's a ghost ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about unscientific...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:30.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lighthouse Keeper -\NKoji Hamada (42)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:33.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Great Detective Kogoro Mori Lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Mori-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!\NThere's still time until the lecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These cooked turban\Nshells are delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, after the lecture,\NI'd like to ask for your help...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:08:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to find\Nwhere the {\i1}Ryujin-Maru {\i0}sank?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such perceptiveness!\NI think it sank near this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we just knew where,\Nwe could locate the missing gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it were recovered,\Nit wouldn't belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The government\Nwould come to collect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't we\Nbe entitled to 10% of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Mori-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! No famous detective\Nwould ever go treasure hunting--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about 10% of\Nthe island's reward money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinoshita! Give him the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened on a stormy\Nnight seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We received an SOS from the\N{\i1}Ryujin-Maru {\i0}about 1 km offshore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:09:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the signal disappeared\Nas a rescue crew headed for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the next day, only the\Nowner's body washed ashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No debris was ever found,\Nmuch less the gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose gold was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship's owner's. He was\Ngoing to be arrested for tax evasion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he converted his entire\Nfortune into gold and was on his way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,out of the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well! I, Kogoro Mori,\Nshall locate the gold for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about this lecture thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he just gonna\Nhumiliate himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Suigun Artifact Museum
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The general's armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! There's so much rare stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's this island's cultural heritage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four-hundred years ago, the Suigun\Nescaped here after being defeated
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a large battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the islanders wanted the\Nreward money for their heads
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and attacked the wounded Suigun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They eventually drove them into\Na remote cave and killed them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Various bad things\Nhave occurred ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. So a shrine was built in the\Ncave to quiet the Suigun's spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't curses just superstitions?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many people who live near the\Ncave have seen armor-clad ghosts,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and eerie groans can be heard\Ncoming from the cave's depths.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was about five years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when a university professor\Nstudying the Suigun visited.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ignored the islanders'\Nwarnings and went to examine the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But two or three nights later...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that professor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It was never confirmed,\Nbut he was never seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody dares go near\Nthat cave anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believing that in this day and\Nage is why you get laughed at!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy said the professor\Nchecked the cave but probably left
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'cause he didn't find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!\NI'll show you a great place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can sneak backstage from here!\NBest seats in the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hamada, the lighthouse keeper.\NHe's really weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hardly hangs out with anyone,\Nand he always goes to that cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time, no see, Aoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pretend you don't recognize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NI'm Hamada, the lighthouse keeper!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the wrong person! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tear that face of yours off, Aoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, here is the peerless\NDetective Kogoro Mori-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will he be all\Nright drunk like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He appears to be rather nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have him break the\Ncelebration ball in honor of his visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever you're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gasoline!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the curse!\NThe Suigun curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. That string was modified\Nto ignite the gasoline inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The target being... the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In which case,\Nthe ones most suspect are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hamada-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nwho left out the back door,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the man he got in\Nan argument with, Uehara-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it have something\Nto do with the ghost ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayor! What's the meaning of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only survived because\NI'm so well-trained!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My deepest apologies for getting\Nyou involved in such an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accident?!\NSomeone clearly planned that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sparks from a short\Ncircuit just happened to ignite
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a nearby gas container--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me. It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you just don't\Nwant a police incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't gonna turn the gold\Nover if you found it, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'd have no choice\Nif the mainland police showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}! You just need to\Nkeep quiet and find the gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defy me and there's no guarantee\Nyou'll leave the island unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't threaten me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't take the ferry\Nwithout my authorization.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take your time\Nto think it over tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we came\Nto a pretty bad island...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinoshita-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize. The mayor seems\Nto only care about finding the gold
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and turning the island\Ninto a tourist attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a selfish bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you back\Nto the mainland anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, I can prepare\Na small fishing boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I refuse to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inadvisable!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be harmed if you stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No self-respecting detective\Nwould dare run away now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well said, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinoshita-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Hamada-{\i1}san{\i0} like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the lighthouse keeper?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know; he's not from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came here a while after\Nthe {\i1}Ryujin-Maru {\i0}incident
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and said he was looking for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no one working the\Nlighthouse, so he took that job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Hamada do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I just thought he seemed strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yoko-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:17:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Hamada-i?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude! You should thank\Nme for following you late at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, we're not that\Nclose of friends yet--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uehara-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was that person up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person was searching the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gasoline. Yet there are\Nno cars or motorcycles here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was Hamada-{\i1}san\N{\i0}who tried to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan! Don't run off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was he doing up here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A telescope?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. There's nothing to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointed at the mountains.\NThey'd be boring to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. A lighthouse\Ntelescope should be pointing out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this one is fixed\Ntoward the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'{\i1}Ryujin-Maru{\i0}'?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No question about it! Hamada-{\i1}san\N{\i0}is connected to the {\i1}Ryujin-Maru{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's something\Nhe doesn't want investigated,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he tried to kill the old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! The old man and Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to run\Nwith my sore butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go?! I was so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad was attacked by a Suigun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The alarm bell by the port!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They ring it whenever\Nsomething happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Did something happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is some sort of mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That detective killed Hamada,\Nthe lighthouse keeper!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check for yourself\Nif you think we're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we arrived on the scene,\Nthe detective was unconscious
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the victim was dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe me! I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ghosts got mad because\Nan outsider was poking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He would never\Ndo something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But given the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.42,0:24:25.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.21,0:24:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinoshita-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.89,0:24:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ghosts are mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.27,0:24:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A suicide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.98,0:24:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this was no suicide!\NIn which case, the killer is--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.44,0:24:31.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ghost Ship Murder Case (Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.15,0:24:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.65,0:24:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ghost Ship Murder Case (Part 2).
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.95,0:24:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.31,0:24:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gunshot Wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.73,0:24:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode the case takes a surprising turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.45,0:24:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, heh, heh. I'm the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.26,0:24:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not you, Genta.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.66,0:24:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
